Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:50.54,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}仰望蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:53.96,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}今亦得见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:59.53,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}逆风疾走 赶上电车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.52,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蕙芷芬芳 色状霓虹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:05.72,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向阳步道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:10.81,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}鹿撞愈疾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:17.94,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}散学廊下 钟声回响
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:21.34,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}无奇世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:25.75,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}渐始闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:32.47,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}走而出者 慕君之思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:38.48,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}眼底心内 如系如缚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:44.30,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}心潮难平 盈溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:50.43,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}重之以君意 可与我知否
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.35,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}此心君可解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:56.26,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}此意望君知
